Name: Yellowstone Wardens
Title: That's What I Shoulda Did
Desc: Tracking down hunters riding their ATV through farmers' crops; a claim of illegal hunting.
LongDescription: Warden Lesofski tracks down hunters riding their ATV through farmers' crops; Warden Taylor investigates a claim of illegal hunting on private property; Warden Golie races to find a hunter disobeying a landowner's rules.
